[SHORT DESC]
Does 1/4 damage per turn at the cost of half the user's max HP if the user is a Ghost. Boosts Atk and Def and lowers Spe 1 stage otherwise.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Does 1/4 damage per turn at the cost of half the user's max HP if the user is a Ghost-type. The effect is removed when the target switches. Boosts Attack and Defense one stage and lowers Speed one stage if the user is not a Ghost-type.</p>

<p>If the user is a Ghost-type, Curse will fail if there are no other Pokemon in play.</p>